    "122790692": {
      "title": "Existence and concentration of solutions for a class of biharmonic equations",
      "abstract": "Abstract Some superlinear fourth order elliptic equations are considered. A family of solutions is proved to exist and to concentrate at a point in the limit. The proof relies on variational methods and makes use of a weak version of the Ambrosetti\u2013Rabinowitz condition. The existence and concentration of solutions are related to a suitable truncated equation."
